headline: WM Announces Cash Dividend
summary: HOUSTON, February 18, 2025--WM (NYSE: WM) today announced the declaration of a quarterly cash dividend of $0.825 per share payable Mar. 28, 2025, to stockholders of record on Mar. 14, 2025.
